content: I've been posting at least 3 times a week, and I've been experimenting with different content types like IGTV, Reels, and Stories. I think my "day in the life" vlog from two weeks ago got a lot of engagement, with 200 likes and 30 comments. I've also noticed that my engagement rate has been higher on Tuesdays and Thursdays, so I'm going to try to prioritize posting on those days going forward.
